info.name: Jewelpet Sunshine
info.description: In Sunshine Academy, there is a class of lost causes known as "the leftovers", the Plum class. Ruby and Kanon Mizushirou navigate through high school life in a fantastical world while juggling their warped friendship with their crush on Mikage Shiraishi.

moreInfo.japanese: ジュエルペット サンシャイン
